title: Nahid 2015 Iranian 720x576p h264 AAC 48KHz Makalakato
description:
There's another print on web with lots of pixelation. This has none. 

Persian spoken with English subtitles attached. 

Won Avenir Prize (Un Certain Regard) at Cannes 2015 and Roger Ebert Award at Chicago IFF 2015. 

Director: Ida Panahandeh
Writers: Arsalan Amiri (screenplay), Ida Panahandeh (screenplay)
Stars: Sareh Bayat, Nasrin Babaei, Pejman Bazeghi

A woman tries to mend the broken pieces of her last life, as she is now involved in a new relationship with a man
